Top Level:
SKILL CATEGORIES == Main focuses for lifemaxxing (current outline: Mental Health, Personal Care,
Household and Chores — see SkillCategories/Properties/Main)
    *Per-category layout (properties pattern)*
    "main page" - overview, skill tasks, goals, resources
    "wishlist" - database of [items] for the [shop] (fields: GUI outline in wishlist file)
    "timescale" for skill tasks with specific dates
    "skill tasks"
    Household and Chores extras: [Shopping List] database + knowledge bases (ingredient list, meals & recipes)
    Mental Health extras: [Journal] database (categories + daily entry template); [WINS LIST] subpage

SKILLS == [skill tasks] within a [skill category]
SKILL TASK == a task that must be completed by a [deadline]
-------
Tracking systems:
EXP == credit for completing a [skill task]

EXP PROGRESS METER == Ratio of [EXP earned] to [EXP required] to complete a [mastery level]

MASTERY LEVELS == [EXP] needed to gain a [mastery level] within a [skill category]

STARDUST == Currency, per [skill category], to unlock items in [shop]

------
Rewards:
ITEMS ==  Products that will be useful to progress in a skill category

UPGRADES == Anything that can be purchased, but is not a specific product,
that will be useful to progress in a skill category

-----
Visualizer & deadline tracker:
MAP == Used for accountability & to visually see task list.
